channel.title: Help with client... logging on problem
channel.description: hey, when i start my source, and i attempt to log onto my moparscape client, my screen turns black, (my cmb prompt thing says im logged on) then i get logged off and in the bottom of the moparscape client it says error: T2 - 126,253,253 - 24,0,0-83 and so on.. please help :)

item.title: Help with client... logging on problem
item.dc:creator: @Symbian Symbian
item.description:
@Symbian wrote:

[quote=“tman915, post:1, topic:327665”]hey, when i start my source, and i attempt to log onto my moparscape client, my screen turns black, (my cmb prompt thing says im logged on) then i get logged off and in the bottom of the moparscape client it says
error: T2 - 126,253,253 - 24,0,0-83 and so on…
please help :)[/quote]

That means you are logging in a server that doesn’t support the Moparscape client. Try downloading a different one.
